But you will still get. um.
his sheep and all his land.

2128
01:35:41.416 --> 01:35:42.250
Miss Hampstead.

2129
01:35:42.375 --> 01:35:43.541
-So that's nice.
-Okay.

2130
01:35:43.666 --> 01:35:44.708
Sorry to bother you.

2131
01:35:45.625 --> 01:35:47.791
See. Ham and I [sighs]

2132
